Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.14,0:00:03.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:10.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.40,0:00:12.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你那是什麼表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:15.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那不是咖啡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.99,0:00:17.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈不是喝不了咖啡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:19.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼要買那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.50,0:00:25.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也差不多要成為大人了 以為自己能喝就買了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:26.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你哪裡像大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:37.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就算是我也有很多地方有成長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:40.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那早苗就能喝了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:43.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我能喝啊 而且還是黑咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.65,0:00:48.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,黑咖啡…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:53.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個換給你喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:00:57.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是 我是大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.82,0:00:58.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:00:59.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.49,0:01:00.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.70,0:01:01.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,快換給我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:04.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:10.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:13.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:16.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嘛 也有喝不了咖啡的大人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:17.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不過你還是個小孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:20.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.19,0:01:31.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大人可不會幹這種事
Comment: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,——op——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:18.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天又被高木同學捉弄了一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:28.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不過 明天一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:30.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:34.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:35.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:38.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天一個人走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:38.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:40.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼 一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:42.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:45.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:50.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是高木同學不是騎車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:52.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我推著就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:56.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,空罐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那罐果汁 是最近新推出的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:04.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:06.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:09.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這難道是什麼陷阱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:10.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你要不要嘗一口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:13.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:14.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:17.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:21.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 雖然我不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:25.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣其實是間接接吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:28.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哼哼哼 怎麼樣啊 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:31.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好意思了吧 你就難為情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:35.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:38.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她一點也不難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:40.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個人究竟怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:42.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,給你 謝謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:43.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真好喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:53.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:57.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喝啊 我完全不介意的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:00.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼 這點小事不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:06.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是間接接吻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:15.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:18.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我看看 垃圾桶在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:21.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:23.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哇哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:26.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 你還真能投進去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:30.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一順手就投出去了 沒想到竟然能投中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:43.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我原來還有這種才能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:47.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 我也來試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:06:02.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你往哪裡扔啊 根本搆不到嘛高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:05.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那你要和我比賽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:07.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比賽？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:09.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,無所謂 反正我是不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:14.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼我們輪流投 先投進者為勝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:18.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,竟然發起沒有勝算的挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:22.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看來高木同學已經氣昏頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:24.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這感覺真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:28.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是高木同學贏了 你要我做什麼我都聽你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:31.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我可聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:33.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,待會兒不准反悔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:34.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:37.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不過我不會輸就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:40.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我要扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:42.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:52.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是你沒投中 就是我的勝利了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:58.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又被她擺了一道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:04.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,站在剛才的位置上 用同樣的角度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:07.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:12.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我能行 我一定能投進去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:13.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是西片贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:18.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我就把我的初吻給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:33.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:35.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:36.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:38.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你還問是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:40.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就在我投的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:41.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:44.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好的 要遵守約定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:48.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要讓你幹什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:58.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 她想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:00.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:04.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就算不讓你做什麼也沒什麼不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:05.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:09.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 高木同學 那不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:11.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你這樣做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:14.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我感覺我一輩子都沒辦法贏過你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:15.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那就有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:16.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,反正你也贏不了我 這不挺好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:20.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你這是什麼意思啊 我說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:23.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,碳酸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:29.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太辣舌頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:29.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}此處日語的「辛い」，專指食物對口腔舌頭的刺激、刺痛感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:30.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你那是什麼表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:32.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那不是碳酸汽水嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:34.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈不是喝不了碳酸汽水嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:40.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,碳酸為什麼會這麼辣舌頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:43.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼總買些自己喝不了的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:45.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又在裝大人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:49.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是呢 我喜歡這個味道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:53.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「嗡」地一下來勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:53.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}日語「ツンてきた」，意為某些味道對鼻腔的強烈刺激後的表情、反應
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:55.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的舌頭 我的舌頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:57.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你真吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:09:00.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉喝了碳酸汽水之後也會這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:01.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:03.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那你喝喝看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:04.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:10.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,腦子絕對會「嗡」的一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:11.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不會啦 不會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:22.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,其實是來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:23.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:27.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「嗡」的一下究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:29.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的會有那種反應嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:32.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好 想打嗝了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:34.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有反應了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:39.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在這種時候打嗝肯定會被她們嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:46.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是我快要忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:50.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,已經忍不住了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:56.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又「嗡」地來勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:02.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,幹嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:03.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:07.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:13.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:21.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,給我走著瞧 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:24.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,加上回家路上被捉弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:26.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天被她捉弄了十五次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:30.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在比賽中出現失誤的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:34.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,作為給自己的懲罰 我會進行十倍的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:38.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我相信這樣做能讓我在下一次奪取勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:40.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:45.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是被捉弄了十五次 乘上十倍就是一百五十次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:49.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,第一次做的話 沒什麼難度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:52.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,總之先做三倍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:59.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一 二 三 四…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:01.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,十八
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:05.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,十九
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:10.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,二十…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:13.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比想像中難多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:14.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,稍微減少一點次數吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:15.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:20.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這是給平日被捉弄了太多次的自己的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:28.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一邊體會痛苦 一邊提高警惕防止下次重蹈覆轍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:31.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,加油啊 我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:34.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肌肉鍛鍊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:41.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的手臂怎麼了 受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:45.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼 只是普通的肌肉酸痛罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:46.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:52.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,別這樣 真的很疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:54.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,剛剛的要算一次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:58.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這時我應該對自己嚴格一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:00.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就記一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:08.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被騙了吧 肌肉酸痛挺嚴重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:12.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這次是的的確確地被捉弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:15.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼突然肌肉酸痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:18.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個 我從昨天開始鍛鍊肌肉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:22.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 要是不三天打魚兩天曬網就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:25.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哼 你就儘管說吧 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:34.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼 今天被高木同學捉弄的次數是二十三次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:36.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這不是比昨天還多了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:42.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一 二 三…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:45.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說回來 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:47.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你還在堅持鍛鍊肌肉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:49.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 姑且有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:52.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誒 你真的堅持下來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:54.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,託你的福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:56.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不過你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:57.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:13:02.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,據說成長期時肌肉鍛鍊過度的話會長不高哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:05.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:08.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說回來 我也好像在哪裡聽說過…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:10.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:12.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是讓高木同學長得比我還高的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:15.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那她不就會更變本加厲地捉弄我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:17.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:21.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不過那好像只是謠言而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:22.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原來是謠言嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:27.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不如說 適度的肌肉鍛鍊可以促進身高發育呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:32.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是這樣 所以你就安心繼續鍛鍊肌肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:34.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我覺得這樣很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:37.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然只有一點點 但感覺你比以前變得結實了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:41.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:46.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 一言不發的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:51.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道說你害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:53.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,害 害羞什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:55.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你臉紅了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:59.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,果然 你害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:02.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的 你幹嘛總是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:04.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都說了 因為你的反應很有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:08.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不過 你比以前結實了是實話哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:12.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,變得有點帥氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:16.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的臉比剛才更紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:18.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是這樣的 是因為天氣太熱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:21.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:22.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我說 等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:24.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,到頭來 今天被她捉弄了五十四次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:26.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算上剛剛那次就是五十五次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:30.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不過 我決定就算不被高木同學捉弄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:33.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,也要堅持鍛鍊肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:36.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,配音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:40.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喬尼先生 今晚要不要來咱家吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:43.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哎呀 這要看工作忙不忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:46.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是很晚才能下班 我就和次郎吃了再回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:50.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然和次郎打好關係也不錯 偶爾也來一下咱家嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:53.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,人家最近很寂寞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:55.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是我要工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:14:59.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,差不多該回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.67,0:15:01.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼 再玩一會兒也沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:05.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼要講關西腔啊 聽到就煩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:09.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太過分了 你一點也不在乎人家的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:11.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你這麼說也太小氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:13.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也是很拼命的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:17.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你哭什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:21.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為 喬尼先生和次郎都陷入工作無法自拔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:24.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,人家已經不能忍耐下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.57,0:15:26.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,突然變成修羅場了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:29.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 真是麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:31.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太過分了 太過分了喬尼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:35.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是你是這種態度的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:37.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我就不管你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:39.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:43.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那兩隻貓 都是公的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:48.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那 應該叫喬尼前輩才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:51.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,呀 這不是次郎嗎 一起去吃飯如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:55.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,回家吧 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:15:58.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,傘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:09.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,竟然在放學時開始下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:12.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼 我可沒聽說今天會下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:15.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我沒帶雨衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:16.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,冒失鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:19.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早苗 你對美奈太嚴格啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:22.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我們搭巴士回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:24.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我沒帶錢搭巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:26.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,超級冒失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:28.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:30.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我借給你吧 巴士票而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:35.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡 今天也被捉弄得夠嗆的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:40.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不回家嗎 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:44.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個 我忘帶傘和雨衣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:50.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你還真是冒失啊 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:52.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不知道今天會下雨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:54.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的太冒失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:16:59.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,竟然沒有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:03.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我記得西片的傘挺大的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:05.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:12.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這就是所謂的相合傘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:14.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼會發生這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:17.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好 感覺這樣好尷尬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:19.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:21.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,說些什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:25.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學 你的自行車怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:27.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我明天走路上學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:30.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:35.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺剛才的氣氛尷尬的要命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:39.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺要窒息了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:42.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不趕緊做些什麼緩和這種氣氛的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:49.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:51.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:53.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:55.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被嚇到了吧 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:01.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:02.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:05.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡 不愧是高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:07.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這種程度的惡作劇…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:09.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼濕噠噠的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:16.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你太大驚小怪了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:25.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說回來 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:27.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你那邊的肩膀淋濕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.91,0:18:30.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只淋濕了一點兒 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:32.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不行 會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:36.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再湊近一點 好好地躲到傘下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:49.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,心臟跳動的聲音 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:51.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:56.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是被高木同學發現我很緊張 她一定會來捉弄我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:59.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,總之 不說些什麼的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:01.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:03.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:07.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學竟然忘記帶傘 真是少見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:11.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道說 高木同學出人意料地是個冒失鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:15.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道我說得太過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:20.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:22.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我可能也有些健忘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:28.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學承認自己有些健忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:31.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這是什麼展開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:33.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺自己好像贏了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:37.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,剛才我也忘了一件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:39.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎 忘了事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:40.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是什麼事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:45.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,像現在這樣 形容兩個人打著同一把傘走路的情形
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:47.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是叫什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:49.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:51.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我有點想不起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:54.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:56.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是叫什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:19:59.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,相合傘…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:01.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:04.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我聽不到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:09.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:12.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是相合傘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:14.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你肯定沒有忘記吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:16.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:18.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個是叫什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:24.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,情侶之間為了表達愛意 用自己的嘴唇去接觸對方嘴唇那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:28.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡 答不上來就輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:30.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,親 親吻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:33.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼 雨聲太大 我聽不見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:36.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雨勢已經比剛才小了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:40.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要裝作沒聽見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:42.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是親吻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:44.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 是的是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:49.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還有 不是有情侶用來表達心情的詞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:50.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:53.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你看 就是那個比「喜歡」更進一步的詞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:55.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:58.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,開頭的第一個字是「a」的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:58.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}這裡高木想說的詞是日語的「我愛你」 即愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:00.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我不知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:03.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,下一個字是「i」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:05.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我猜不出來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:07.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼 換成英文的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:09.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是「I」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.78,0:21:11.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,接下來是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:18.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「I」「lo」的下一個字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:21.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你說說看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:23.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,已經夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:25.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,最後一個字是「you」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:26.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:30.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:41.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雨停了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.61,0:21:42.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:46.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好了 我還以為要堅持到高木同學家門口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:48.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,害得我提心弔膽的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:51.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:53.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我走這邊回去 再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:59.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我忘記回家的路了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.09,0:22:04.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的 饒了我吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPJP——
