Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.36,0:22:37.71,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}推開窗戶 你的秀髮隨微風飄揚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.04,0:22:42.13,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}走出房間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.13,0:22:48.80,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你挽著我的手臂 輕聲呢喃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.88,0:22:57.89,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}「再陪我一會兒 再陪我一會兒」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.89,0:23:09.99,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}我要把這思念傳達給你 在世界被染上黑暗之前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.03,0:23:17.75,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}所以拜託了 請留在我身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.79,0:23:20.08,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}因為我是如此地愛著你
